title: Conquest of Australia EU4 mod
description:
Conquest of Australia EU4 mod

Extract rar file to your 'C:Users[user]Documents Paradox Interactive Europa Universalis IV mod' folder


DESCRIPTION
Conquest of Australia brings Conquest of Paradise mechanics to Australia and New Zealand. 

NEW: Maori nations, culture, national ideas and formable union. 

Features include: 
Playable Aboriginal nations with Native mechanics 
Australian colonail region with unique names for British, French, Dutch, and 
Malay cultures. 
Formable nations of Australia and New Zealand 
Expanded Aboriginal culture
